{
  "_comment": "Refreshable logo manifest for decks. Resolves each brand's official logo from Wikidata (property P154 'logo image') via a search term, then downloads from Wikimedia Commons. 'commons' overrides with an explicit Commons filename; 'url' with a direct download; 'local' copies an existing file (path relative to this dir). Re-run refresh_logos.py to pull the latest. Naming: <category>-<type>-<Name>.<ext>, where type defaults to 'logo' (product connector UI icons use 'icon'). Categories: datasource (warehouses/DBs/storage/connectors + syndicated data providers), bi (BI/semantic/catalog tools), cloud (cloud platforms), comms (messaging/destinations), customer, output, brand (first-party Tellius/Kaiya marks; 'self: true', committed directly with no external refresh source).",
